    "Finally, our current model only includes cortical area V1.",
    "Because of the configuration of the cortical surface, it is much easier to implant electrodes in higher-level visual areas such as areas V2 or V3.",
    "Many aspects of our model, including the transformation from visual space to cortical surface 63, 65, 92, will easily generalize to these higher visual areas."
